  "prompt": "I'm new to Quora. What does it mean when someone says they are following me?",
  "response": "Welcome to Quora! When someone says they are following you on Quora, it means they are interested in the content you post or the questions you answer, and they want to receive updates about your activity. By following you, they can easily see your new answers, posts, and questions in their feed. It's a way for users to stay connected and engage with content they find valuable or interesting. If you have further questions about using Quora, feel free to ask!",
